                <h2>Why Ament Law Group?</h2>
                <p>Ament Law Group, P.C. is a growing law firm in Murrysville, Pennsylvania, serving families and businesses across six counties in Western Pennsylvania. We are committed to building a team of talented professionals who share our values of trust, service, and excellence.</p>
                <p>Our firm offers the opportunity to work in a collaborative, community-oriented environment with experienced attorneys across estate planning, probate, real estate, business law, and elder law. We invest in our team members' professional development and believe in maintaining a healthy work-life balance.</p>

                <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Competitive compensation</li>
                    <li>Professional development and mentorship</li>
                    <li>Collaborative, supportive work environment</li>
                    <li>Opportunity to make a meaningful impact in the community</li>
                    <li>Convenient Murrysville location on Route 22</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Current Openings</h2>
                <p>We are always looking for talented individuals to join our team. Even if no positions are listed below, we encourage you to reach out — we keep qualified candidates in mind for future opportunities.</p>

